# A person travels 1825kms in a year and can go more 6kms in a leap year. Ask the user to enter a year and find the travelled distance for that year.

year = int(input("Enter a year: "))

if (year % 400 == 0) or (year % 4 == 0 and year % 100 != 0):
    distance = 1825 + 6
else:
    distance = 1825

print("Total distance travelled in the year", year, "is", distance, "kms")

# OUTPUT 
'''
Enter a year: 2024
Total distance travelled in the year 2024 is 1831 kms
'''
